{"tid":1896240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020dse 反抗","createTime":"2020-02-25T04:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T06:40:14.000Z","uid":337228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3824da8dc8632b5cd49066a23b060c4f3fdf7cca","tid":1896240,"uid":337228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:32:51.000Z","msg":"暫時有消息指教育局有意決定如期進行<br />\n消息：文憑試筆試如期3月27日開考<br />\n<br />\n教育局及考評局下午開記者會，講述有關學校及文憑試的安排。消息指，當局決定採納第一個方案，即文憑試各科筆試如期在3月27日展開。根據考評局早前公布的第一個方案，文憑試各科筆試及英文科口試如期在3月27日展開，體育及音樂實習考試延至5月舉行。中文科口試延至5月18日至26日舉行，而放榜日期就會延後至7月15日。教育局局長楊潤雄及考試及評核局秘書長蘇國生下午 2時會見傳媒，公布有關學校及香港中學文憑考試的安排。<br />\n<br />\n2020-02-25 11:57:57<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家想攬左定係自己決定命運</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲有中學生關注組先前嘅問卷我想知道結果如何 如果大家推比中學生關注組 等佢快啲發表結果</span>"},{"pid":"2599a8be2d339388084f1fee58a7b9c314041918","tid":1896240,"uid":24467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"推啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ff52f9dcce4a8c5c13151b9edefa4dd52401e0","tid":1896240,"uid":337228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXeKau2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXeKau2.png&h=1307bd95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請大家多多留意 包括中六生及應屆考生"},{"pid":"9cbe70eb184320fa5d5cad21d4e779995a2fa2a0","tid":1896240,"uid":337228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"9f086a5486321aae635c94f67b643e64094eb7f5","tid":1896240,"uid":337228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"ea8581d7bd7a48b7b6953fa37cc3c803156248cd","tid":1896240,"uid":337228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T04:44:22.000Z","msg":"推3/10"},{"pid":"925d951f98db50ef21c849e6920ccf14c26d51f5","tid":1896240,"u